\v 1 Ngomnyaka\x + 8.22. Jer. 4.23. Lilo 3.2. Hez. 32.7,8.\x* wokufa kwenkosi uUziya\x + 1.1. 2 Lan. 26.22.\x* ngabona iNkosi ihlezi esihlalweni sobukhosi\x + Joha. 12.41. 1 Kho. 22.19.\x* esiphezulu lesiphakemeyo, lemiphetho yesembatho sayo yagcwalisa ithempeli.
\v 2 \w Amaserafi\w** ayemi ngaphezu kwayo; impiko eziyisithupha\x + Isam. 4.8.\x*, impiko eziyisithupha zalelo lalelo; ngezimbili lagubuzela ubuso balo, langezimbili lagubuzela inyawo zalo, langezimbili laphapha.
\p
\v 3 Lelinye lamemeza kwelinye lathi: Ingcwele, ingcwele, ingcwele iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla\x + Isam. 4.8. Joha. 17.1.\x*; umhlaba wonke ugcwele inkazimulo yayo\x + Isam. 4.8. Joha. 17.1.\x*\x + Hlab. 72.19.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Insika zomnyango zasezinyikinyeka ngenxa yelizwi lomemezayo, lendlu yagcwala intuthu\x + Eks. 19.18. Isam. 15.8. Eks. 40.34. Hlab. 18.7,8.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Ngasengisithi: Maye kimi\x + Eks. 3.6. 6.30. Jer. 1.6. Hlu. 6.22. Luka 5. 8.\x*, ngoba ngiyabhubha! Ngoba ngingumuntu wendebe ezingcolileyo, futhi ngihlala phakathi kwabantu bendebe ezingcolileyo; ngoba amehlo ami abonile iNkosi, uJehova wamabandla\x + 33.17.\x*.
\v 6 Kwasekuphaphela kimi elinye lamaserafi lilelahle elivuthayo esandleni salo \add e\add*lali\add li\add*thethe ngodlawu elathini\x + Isam. 6.9. 8.3.\x*.
\v 7 Lathinta umlomo wami\x + Jer. 1.9. Dan. 10.16.\x*, lathi: Khangela, lokhu kuzithintile indebe zakho; ngakho ububi bakho bususiwe, lesono sakho senzelwe inhlawulo lokuthula\x + 22.14. 27.9. Hlab. 65.3.\x*.
\v 8 Ngasengisizwa ilizwi leNkosi lisithi: Ngizathuma bani? Njalo ngubani ozasiyela?\x + Gen. 1.26. Hez. 21.10.\x* Ngasengisithi: Khangela, ngi\add lapha\add*, thuma mina\x + 1 Sam. 3.4.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Yasisithi: Hamba, uthi kulababantu: Zwanini lizwe\x + Mat. 13.14. Mark. 4.12. Luka 8.10. Joha. 12.40.\x*, kodwa kaliyikuqedisisa; njalo bonani libone, kodwa kaliyikubonisisa.
\v 10 Yenza inhliziyo yalababantu ikhuluphale\x + 63.17. Hlab. 119.70.\x*, wenze indlebe zabo zibe nzima, uvale amehlo abo\x + 29.10. Hlab. 69.23.\x*, hlezi babone ngamehlo abo\x + Jer. 5.21.\x*, bezwe ngendlebe zabo, baqedisise ngenhliziyo zabo, baphenduke, babesebesiliswa.
