\v 11 Ngasengisithi: Koze kube nini, Nkosi?\x + Hlab. 79.5. 89.46.\x* Yasisithi: Kuze kuchitheke imizi ingabi lamhlali, lezindlu zingabi lamuntu, lelizwe lichitheke lithi nya,
\v 12 leN\nd kosi\nd* ibasusele khatshana abantu\x + 26.15. 2 Kho. 25.21.\x*, njalo kube lokutshiywa okukhulu phakathi kwelizwe.
\v 13 Kodwa ingxenye eyodwa etshumini\x + 10.21,22,11. 17.6. 46.3. 1.9.\x* isezakuba kulo; izaphenduka, ibe ngeyokudliwa\x + 5.5. Nani 24.22.\x*; \w njengomtherebhinti\w**\x + 1.30.\x* lanjengesihlahla \w se-okhi\w**, esiwohloza amahlamvu aso, isidindi saso sikuzo\x + 1 Lan. 26.16.\x*; inzalo engcwele\x + 11.1. Ezra 9.2. Mal. 2.15.\x* iyisidindi salo.
